text: İslamköy may refer to: *İslamköy, a former name of Banaz, a town in Uşak Province, Turkey *İslamköy, Kastamonu, a village in Kastamonu Province, Turkey *İslamköy, Devrek, a village in Devrek District, Zonguldak Province, Turkey *İslamköy, Kahta, a village in the District of Kahta, Adıyaman Province
title: İslamköy
